[{"id":"VR797930","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows 2 views of a slab. One view shows the slab has a thickness of 2 z sub 0. The other view shows the slab in the x y z coordinate system occupying the region negative z sub 0 less than or equal to z, less than or equal to z sub 0.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR797930.g02.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The figure shows an infinite slab of thickness <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 z sub 0\"><math alttext=\"2 z sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span> that occupies the region <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative z sub 0 is less than or equal to z, which is less than or equal to z sub 0\"><math alttext=\"negative z sub 0 is less than or equal to z, which is less than or equal to z sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>≤</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>≤</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span> in an <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x y z\"><math alttext=\"x y z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><mi>z</mi></math></span></span> coordinate system. The charge density <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"rho\"><math alttext=\"rho\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>ρ</mi></math></span></span> of the slab varies with <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"z\"><math alttext=\"z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>z</mi></math></span></span> according to the equation <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"rho of z equals, C times the absolute value of z\"><math alttext=\"rho of z equals, C times the absolute value of z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>ρ</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>C</mi><mrow><mo>|</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>|</mo></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>C</mi></math></span></span> is a positive constant and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the absolute value of z is less than or equal to z sub 0\"><math alttext=\"the absolute value of z is less than or equal to z sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mo>|</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>≤</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>. The magnitude of the electric field at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"plus or minus z\"><math alttext=\"plus or minus z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mo>±</mo><mi>z</mi></math></span></span> is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"E sub 0\"><math alttext=\"E sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>. What is the magnitude of the electric field at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"z equals, plus or minus the fraction z sub 0 over 2\"><math alttext=\"z equals, plus or minus the fraction z sub 0 over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span>?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR797930_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one fourth E sub 0\"><math alttext=\"one fourth E sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one half E sub 0\"><math alttext=\"one half E sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"E sub 0\"><math alttext=\"E sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 E sub 0\"><math alttext=\"2 E sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>E</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":0}]